channel.title: Confused? :S
channel.description:
Well, I just joined to post this :| I'm not even sure if this is the right section :(
But anyway, I've been trying to post my server onto the server status page, and it says my server is already posted on there, and for me to look again. So I go look, and I find nothing. Even with ctrl + f i dont find anything. I searched in the online and offline server status. What am I doing wrong? :S Btw my server is on.
